data.description: Come in and make yourself at home! Take advantage of this wonderful opportunity to own a home in the sought after Ledgewick Subdivision. Step into this immaculate, former model home built to GOLD FORTFIED standard by DSLD Homes on an oversized corner lot. Only 2 years old, this home features upgrades galore with extensive molding and curated designer lighting throughout by Hollis Interiors and Vesta Taylor Design. Recessed lighting in kitchen, living room, and all guest bedrooms. Take note at the beautiful kitchen with granite counter tops, striking stained cabinets, and stainless appliances - making this an entertainers paradise. Many features throughout including 4 Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths with a large primary suite and primary Bath, LVP flooring throughout (NO CARPET). This home also features a fully fenced yard great for pets and privacy. Don’t miss the opportunity to assume the mortgage at a favorable interest rate of 5.25% through Stockton Mortgage! Seller is Licensed Real Estate Agent in State of Alabama.
